snippet.textDisplay: I don't know who's gonna relate this with me. I believe this song is what I was waiting for. Yes, i wanted to hear it from someone that it's the prime time to get up and focus on my life as no one would do it for me. i have to do it by my own. I have to be strong enough to face this world. I won't stop. I wont Quit I'll open my wings without the fear of falling down. Who's gonna be better than Maestro @SajjadAli himself saying it to me "Bus Kaafi hogaye yaaar do laina de wich kaar" Hats of to the lyricist, Composition Story telling production and Yes @Xulfi respect earned + Mission Accomplished. 👏👏👏
